OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772917927
OL,3,CWales defeated in Dublin as Ireland
OL,4,Ckeep Six Nations title hopes alive
OL,6,FIreland kept alive their slim hopes of
OL,7,Freclaiming the Guinness Six Nations
OL,8,Ftitle by battling to a 27-17 bonus-
OL,9,Fpoint victory against winless Wales in
OL,10,FDublin.
OL,12,FFirst-half tries from Jacob Stockdale
OL,13,Fand Jack Crowley put Andy Farrell's
OL,14,Fside on course to set up a Triple
OL,15,FCrown showdown with Scotland next
OL,16,Fweekend.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
