PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772917927
OL,3,CWales defeated in Dublin as Ireland
OL,4,Ckeep Six Nations title hopes alive
OL,6,FAlthough Ireland remain in contention
OL,7,Ffor championship glory, table-topping
OL,8,FFrance will retain the title with a
OL,9,Fround to spare by beating Scotland
OL,10,Fwith a bonus point at Murrayfield on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,FWales, meanwhile, will bid to avoid
OL,14,Fthe wooden spoon for the third
OL,15,Fsuccessive Six Nations when they host
OL,16,FItaly on the final weekend following a
OL,17,Fcreditable display at the Aviva
OL,18,FStadium.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
