PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772917927
OL,3,CWales defeated in Dublin as Ireland
OL,4,Ckeep Six Nations title hopes alive
OL,6,FSteve Tandy's side crossed the Irish
OL,7,FSea heartened by a promising
OL,8,Fperformance in a 26-23 loss to
OL,9,FScotland last time out and with
OL,10,Fgenuine belief of causing an upset.
OL,12,FYet Welsh hopes of a first Six Nations
OL,13,Fwin in Dublin since 2012 were dealt a
OL,14,Fblow inside six minutes as Stockdale
OL,15,Fburst on to a Stuart McCloskey pass to
OL,16,Fclaim his 20th international try.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
