PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772917927
OL,3,CWales defeated in Dublin as Ireland
OL,4,Ckeep Six Nations title hopes alive
OL,6,FIreland hit back within five minutes
OL,7,Fand had the bonus point in the bag
OL,8,Fwhen full-back Osborne finished a fine
OL,9,Fteam move with his third try in as
OL,10,Fmany games.
OL,12,FWales scrum-half Tomos Williams was
OL,13,Fsin-binned for an infringement in the
OL,14,Fbuild-up, while Crowley's poor miss
OL,15,Ffrom the conversion attempt left his
OL,16,Fteam protecting only a seven-point
OL,17,Fadvantage going into the final 10
OL,18,Fminutes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
